snippet.title: Fruit Machine Mania - PlayStation 2 Gameplay
snippet.description:
Published by Oxygen Interactive under the Liquid Games label, this is exactly what the name says: a collection of slot machines. And yes, this shovelware title DID manage to get released in the UK PlayStation Store as a "PS2 Classic" for the PlayStation 3.
